Can you create a JSON data format for a story about Susan and Mark set in a bustling city street?
Here is an example JSON data format for the story:
{
  "title": "Susan and Mark's Adventure in the City",
  "characters": [
    {
      "name": "Susan",
      "description": "A young woman in her early twenties with short curly hair and bright blue eyes. She is wearing a red dress and carrying a large tote bag.",
      "actions": [
        {
          "description": "Susan stops to admire a street performer playing the guitar.",
          "time": "10:00am"
        },
        {
          "description": "Susan and Mark grab a quick lunch at a food cart.",
          "time": "12:30pm"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Mark",
      "description": "A tall man in his mid-twenties with short brown hair and green eyes. He is wearing a blue shirt and jeans.",
      "actions": [
        {
          "description": "Mark spots a trendy coffee shop and suggests they stop for a drink.",
          "time": "9:30am"
        },
        {
          "description": "Mark leads Susan through a crowded marketplace, pointing out interesting items for sale.",
          "time": "2:00pm"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "setting": {
    "description": "The city street is bustling with activity. There are street performers, food vendors, and crowds of people rushing by.",
    "time": "Daytime"
  }
}
